      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="add_section" data-step-uuid="EA3888AF-B34B-4EE5-AFB2-342D62A64EBE">
    <h2 id="add_section" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Add Section</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/000/777/291/original/7bf49a42-5d9a-4708-a7a3-04a8b8ea74fa.png" srcset="" alt="Add Section" height="250" width="200">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_0D0690C0-215E-0135-FD8A-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To create a new ePortfolio Section, click the <strong>Add Section</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="add_section_name" data-step-uuid="FD8BE54E-527B-4AA5-93EB-B5D920993301">
    <h3 id="add_section_name" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Add Section Name</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/000/777/281/original/cbac0268-a108-44c2-852e-bfb8327c0282.png" srcset="" alt="Add Section Name" height="303" width="204">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_0D076380-215E-0135-FD8C-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Type your new section name in the section name field. Press Return (on a Mac keyboard ) or Enter (on a PC keyboard). </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="manage_sections" data-step-uuid="20E76050-2AD0-447A-8A01-9FCEF91C86C1">
    <h2 id="manage_sections" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Manage Sections</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/000/777/283/original/282b3e0d-5fc8-44fc-9a16-78c461ff65fe.png" srcset="" alt="Manage Sections" height="287" width="265">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_0D07F0D0-215E-0135-FD8E-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To edit any section, click the <strong>Settings</strong> menu. To rename a section, click the <strong>Rename</strong> link [1]. To delete a section, click the <strong>Delete</strong> link [2]. To move a section, click the <strong>Move to...</strong> link [3]. You can also rearrange sections by clicking and dragging them.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

